HEADWORD: Unearthly
<hw>Un*earth"ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not terrestrial; supernatural;
preternatural; hence, weird; appalling; terrific; <as>as, an
<ex>unearthly</ex> sight or sound</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un*earth"li*ness</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unease</ent>⟦br⟧
